---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dashboard - ContentAI" description="Quản lý tài khoản ContentAI của bạn.">
  <Header />

  <section class="dashboard">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="dashboard-header">
        <div class="dashboard-kicker">Control Center</div>
        <h1>Quản lý website, quota và license trong một bảng điều khiển gọn.</h1>
        <p>Chọn website, theo dõi quota miễn phí, gắn key Pro và tải plugin ngay từ cùng một màn hình.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="dashboard-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="card-title">Tài khoản</h2>
          <div class="user-info">
            <div class="user-avatar">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H8a4 4 0 00-4 4v2M12 11a4 4 0 100-8 4 4 0 000 8z" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="account-label">Tài khoản Google</p>
              <p class="account-status" id="userStatus">Đang tải thông tin...</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card-wide">
          <div class="card-header-row">
            <h2 class="card-title card-title-clean">Website của tôi</h2>
            <span class="badge badge-free" id="tierBadge" style="display: none;">Free</span>
          </div>
          <p class="section-note">
            Mỗi website có trạng thái riêng. Free sẽ theo quota tháng, Pro sẽ theo license key đã kích hoạt.
          </p>

          <div id="domainList" class="domain-list">
            <div class="loading-state">
              <svg class="spin" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 2v4M12 18v4M4.93 4.93l2.83 2.83M16.24 16.24l2.83 2.83M2 12h4M18 12h4M4.93 19.07l2.83-2.83M16.24 7.76l2.83-2.83" stroke="#0f766e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              </svg>
              <span>Đang tải danh sách website...</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <form id="addDomainForm" class="add-domain-form">
            <div class="input-group" style="flex: 1;">
              <input
                type="url"
                id="newDomain"
                name="newDomain"
                class="input"
                placeholder="https://yoursite.com"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="input-group" style="width: 220px;">
              <input
                type="text"
                id="newLicenseKey"
                name="newLicenseKey"
                class="input"
                placeholder="License Key (tùy chọn)"
              />
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="addDomainBtn">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 5v14M5 12h14" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              </svg>
              Thêm website
            </button>
          </form>

          <div id="formMessage" class="alert" style="display: none; margin-top: 16px;"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="card-title">Quota website</h2>
          <div id="usageOverview">
            <div class="usage-total">
              <div class="usage-number" id="totalUsageCount">--</div>
              <div class="usage-label" id="usageLabel">website đang chọn</div>
            </div>
            <div class="usage-bar">
              <div class="usage-bar-fill" id="usageBarFill" style="width: 0%"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="usage-meta">
              <span id="usageRemaining">-- / -- còn lại</span>
              <span id="usageMonth"></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="upgradePrompt" class="upgrade-prompt" style="display: none;">
            <p>Đã dùng hết quota miễn phí.</p>
            <a href="/#pricing" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Nâng cấp Pro</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="card-title">Tải Plugin</h2>
          <p class="section-note">
            Luồng nhanh nhất là tải file zip, cài vào WordPress rồi kết nối domain ngay trong dashboard này.
          </p>

          <div class="download-box">
            <div class="download-info-row">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="#15211b" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <p class="download-file">contentai-plugin.zip</p>
                <p class="download-version" id="pluginVersion">WordPress 6.0+</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a href="/plugin.zip" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 10px 20px;" id="downloadBtn" download>
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M7 10l5 5 5-5M12 15V3" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              </svg>
              Tải về
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="install-guide">
            <h4>Hướng dẫn cài đặt</h4>
            <ol>
              <li>Tải plugin về máy</li>
              <li>Vào WordPress → Plugins → Add New → Upload</li>
              <li>Upload file zip và Activate</li>
              <li>Vào Settings → nhập Domain và License Key nếu có</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  import { initDashboard } from '../lib/dashboard.ts';
  import { runtimeConfig } from '../lib/runtime.ts';

  initDashboard(runtimeConfig);
</script>

<style is:global>
  .dashboard {
    padding: 42px 0 72px;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 72px);
  }

  .dashboard-header {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    padding: 36px 38px;
    border-radius: 36px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at right top, rgb(219 122 57 / 0.18), transparent 24%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(21 33 27 / 0.96) 0%, rgb(15 118 110 / 0.9) 100%);
    color: #fff8ef;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .dashboard-kicker {
    display: inline-flex;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.12);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .dashboard-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff8ef;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    max-width: 14ch;
    line-height: 0.98;
  }

  .dashboard-header p {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgb(255 248 239 / 0.76);
    max-width: 56ch;
  }

  .dashboard-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .card-wide {
    grid-column: span 2;
  }

  .card-header-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-950);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(21 33 27 / 0.08);
  }

  .card-title-clean {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section-note {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .user-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .user-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--primary-light);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .account-label {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-950);
  }

  .account-status {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
  }

  .domain-list {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .domain-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px;
    background: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.72);
    border-radius: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border: 1px solid rgb(21 33 27 / 0.08);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .domain-item:hover {
    border-color: rgb(15 118 110 / 0.18);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .domain-item.active {
    border-color: rgb(15 118 110 / 0.2);
    background: rgb(215 244 239 / 0.34);
  }

  .domain-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .domain-icon {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: rgb(247 242 233 / 0.88);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid rgb(21 33 27 / 0.08);
  }

  .domain-details h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-950);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    word-break: break-word;
  }

  .domain-details span {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
  }

  .domain-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .domain-usage {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
  }

  .delete-btn {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--ink-600);
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .delete-btn:hover {
    background: rgb(220 91 67 / 0.1);
    color: var(--danger);
  }

  .add-domain-form {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .add-domain-form .input-group {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .usage-total {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .usage-number {
    font-size: 56px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-950);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .usage-label {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .usage-bar {
    height: 10px;
    background: rgb(21 33 27 / 0.08);
    border-radius: 999px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .usage-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), #48a295);
    border-radius: 999px;
    transition: width 0.5s ease;
  }

  .usage-meta {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
  }

  .upgrade-prompt {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--accent-soft);
    border-radius: 18px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .upgrade-prompt p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #8c4f21;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .btn-sm {
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .download-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(247 242 233 / 0.82) 0%, rgb(255 255 255 / 0.72) 100%);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 18px;
    gap: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgb(21 33 27 / 0.08);
  }

  .download-info-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .download-file {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-950);
  }

  .download-version {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-600);
  }

  .install-guide {
    margin-top: 18px;
  }

  .install-guide h4 {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--ink-950);
  }

  .install-guide ol {
    padding-left: 20px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
  }

  .loading-state {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 40px;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    color: var(--ink-600);
  }

  .empty-state svg {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .spin {
    animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .dashboard-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .card-wide {
      grid-column: span 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .dashboard-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .card-wide {
      grid-column: span 1;
    }

    .dashboard-header {
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .add-domain-form {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .add-domain-form .input-group {
      width: 100% !important;
    }

    .download-box {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .domain-item {
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .domain-actions {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .usage-number {
      font-size: 46px;
    }

    .usage-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
